divs: Sighting DetailsI had just finished working out at the local gym and was walking home on August 2, 2010. It was a very cloudy day with the potential of storms. I looked up at the clouds when I was walking infront of the local bank and saw the clouds looked awesome so I quickly took a picture on my iPhone and continued on my way. Two weeks later on August 14, 2010 I was looking through the pictures on my iPhone when i noticed on the cloud picture, after the menu bar went away, that their was a weird object in between the hydro lines. I really dont know how to explain this picture, it honestly doesnt look like a bird and thats the only thing that would be flying in the air because I know there were no plaines in the air at that time.
Summary: Took a picture of some weird clouds and a couple weekes later I noticed there was a weird object in the picture I couldn't explain.
